'''Force blinding''',<ref name="Galaxies Card">{{SWGTCG|set=The Shadow Syndicate|cardname=Force Blinding}}</ref> or '''Blind''', was a [[The Force/Legends|Force]] [[Force power/Legends|power]] classified by the [[Sith/Legends|Sith]] as part of the [[Offense]] school of abilities. The technique produced a burst of Force energy that overwhelmed a target's [[Eye/Legends|optic]] nerves, causing temporary blindness.<ref name="Book of Sith">''[[Book of Sith: Secrets from the Dark Side]]''</ref>

A powerful tool of the [[Light side of the Force/Legends|light side]], a [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] could obfuscate an opponent's sight, making it difficult for the adversary to spot and attack the Jedi or anyone else. However, a trained [[Force-sensitive/Legends|Force-sensitive]] who had prepared themselves could defend against this technique by using [[Force sight]]. Still, if the Jedi could blind an unprepared enemy before they reached out with Force Sight, the blind could still be effective. Although it was classically a light side power, both the [[Dark Jedi/Legends|Dark Jedi]] [[Yun]] and the Force apparition [[Dark Mara]] were able to use it.

